      m_Calls: []
  m_text: 'There are two different types of T-Spins: T-Spin Double and T-Spin Triple.


    T-Spin
    Double clears two lines while T-Spin Triple clears three.


    Let''s learn
    about T-Spin Double.


    To execute T-Spin Double you need a T-shaped hole
    and a "ceiling."'
